skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: meal ideas
des: With Meal Ideas, Alexa will help you figure out what to make for your next meal. Simply ask Alexa to start Meal Ideas and Alexa will give you some meal options. This skill is helpful for those times when you just can't think of something to make.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
